title: Teams that Can't Catch a Break
description:
Wendi Nix, Greg McElroy, and Joey Galloway discuss Wisconsin's second cancelled game of the shortened season, D.J. Uiagalelei's debut, Demarcus Thomas' serious injury at Ole Miss, and a look at Michigan's season.
